==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Culmination
<hw>Cul"mi*na"tion</hw> <pr>(k⟦ucr⟧l`m?-n?"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F.<ets>culmination</ets>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
attainment of the highest point of altitude reached by a heavenly body;
passage across the meridian; transit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Attainment or arrival at the highest pitch of glory,
power, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>culottes</ent>⟦br⟧
